'''''Blazing Sun, Illuminate the Path for the Lost''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[Back to Earth in Evernight]].

==Steps==
# Head to Dawncloud
# Defeat the ichor memosprite
# Head to Dawncloud
# Touch the world-cleansing golden blood and summon your friend

