===Touch the world-cleansing golden blood and summon your friend{{subst:void|<!--104367306-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=trailblaze|location="Lightless Chapel" Dawncloud|update|Sing, O Aeon! Sing of the rage of Khaslana, son of Amphoreus&mdash;<br />A drop of burning, cleansing golden blood, melting into your sun-like blazing form.<br /><br />Before that drop of golden blood fell, hatred had long since consumed you. That lengthy journey made our time together feel but a fleeting moment.<br />After that drop of golden blood fell, you've remained silent for far too long. Does your mind still hold its tenacity? Does your defiance still persist?<br />Answer me, for I need a friend to clear the fog and unveil the sun&mdash;<br /><br />If your "guidance" is destined to bring rage that destroys heaven and earth, so be it, as I need a direction forward.<br />Answer me, for only the Dawn's furor can pierce through the evernight.}}
{{Dialogue Start}}
:{{tx}}
{{Dialogue End}}

